{"tid":1467571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［機場事件］正面文宣方向及文章（ＦＢ）入黎用１分鐘ＬＩＫＥ，要贏唔要書！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:40.000Z","uid":219277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6746ff1b3a200ca8ad70f51598983eb26abe6867","tid":1467571,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:51.000Z","msg":"歡迎回覆留低要吹正面風嘅ＰＯＳＴ<br />\n我要聽朝起身一碌ＦＢ全部都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正面野</span></strong><br />\n唔要書書書，書你老味！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2200556136738253/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2200556136738253%2F&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=e8eb3df8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2200556136738253/</a><br />\n（呢個ＰＯＳＴ係俾＂心＂唔係ＬＩＫＥ）<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">今日機場突然變得超級混亂\n再配合一堆網軍係咁散播「輸晒」言論\n影響好多中立派覺得大勢已去\n麻煩唔割嘅人俾個心心穩定軍心</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1760328867642805/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F295202647488775%2Fpermalink%2F1760328867642805%2F&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=f05c1703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1760328867642805/</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">今晚完全係一個公關show, 前兩日警察完全冇藉口去清場因為係一個和平示威活動，再加上射爆眼、葵芳同太古事件，如果當時清場只會比人話警察唔啱，為咗顧及警隊形象，警隊已經安排好成套劇本: \n1~首先機管局停飛所有飛機令到好多旅行團取消，出唔到發嘅人好自然唔應同班示威者\n2~咁啱今日先有民陣講完話機場示威好和平\n3~咁啱今日有外藉人事對示威者大吵大鬧，又話香港本來就屬於中國令到現場人事情緒開始有啲高漲\n4~咁啱懷疑有人過自己係公安\n5~咁啱身上有木棍\n6~咁啱有人著咗記者衫\n7~咁啱又有件I love Hk警察\n\n而且今日啲示威者比起之前嗰啲更情緒高漲，好明顯擺明攪事， 成件事點睇就自己分析一下啦&hellip;最後只會比警察有藉口入去暴力清場。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10157945328917448/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.170516952447%2F10157945328917448%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=efa44fb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10157945328917448/?type=3</a><br />\n蘋果報導<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">【2355 機場】被圍《環時》記者藏撐警T拒認傳媒\n\n一名中年男子被指假冒記者，被抗爭者用索帶鎖起雙手，並被搜出持有一本付姓男子的內地護照、一張雙程證和一名香港警察的卡片。他接受《蘋果》直播訪問時，對鏡頭舉起V字手勢，自稱遊客。《蘋果》在網上搜尋該男子的姓名，發現其名字與中共喉舌《環球時報》記者相符。不過他之前被抗爭者問及是否記者，一直拒絕回答。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=513448716072445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D513448716072445&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=f8fa8962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=513448716072445</a><br />\n呢個係立場影到ＰＯＰＯ撲跌一位女士，義士救人先打ＰＯＰＯ<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onccgongnedi/videos/1096204317237732/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fonccgongnedi%2Fvideos%2F1096204317237732%2F&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=89abc2e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/onccgongnedi/videos/1096204317237732/</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">返悉尼連續2日受阻 「呢啲唔方便只係雞毛」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外岩岩開左個ＰＯＳＴ<br />\n歡迎參考方向<br />\n［文宣方向／準備］狗改不了吃屎，今晚機場又係福建幫ｘ黑狗ｘ公安，破壞機場和理非！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDKHuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDKHuS</a>"},{"pid":"3543632f61f4d3b956dfb5a71cbfc2fceed15676","tid":1467571,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"文宣要贏要正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4e37ef831073d4d80fcce0fda23bcba5c49c4d","tid":1467571,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:50.000Z","msg":"文宣要贏要正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 